      "writtenOn": "2020-11-06T22:38:20Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If all you care about is the warning, I\u0027d be happy to land something that switches these to explicit std::memory_order_seq_cst right away.  Come to think of it, why don\u0027t we do that first, and then look at relaxing anything as follow ups?",
